data.description: HOLIDAY OPEN HOUSE 12-9 10am- 1pm Centrally located in Yucca Valley, a beautiful and well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with a large 18,000+ sq ft lot is ready for your family. This home features 1803 sq ft of living space, open concept floor plan, with formal dining area between livingroom and kitchen, well appointed kitchen with granite counter tops, large pantry, lots of cabinet space, separate laundry room with abundant storage. The master suite features a walk-in closet, hug master bath with separate soaking tub, walk-in shower and double vanity. The backyard features block wall fencing, two beautiful Joshua Trees to enjoy along with the gorgeous mountain views. This home has been lovingly cared for, you will not be disappointed.
